properties.headline: Dense Fog Advisory issued January 14 at 10:43PM EST until January 15 at 9:00AM EST by NWS Tallahassee FL
properties.description:
* WHAT...Dense fog will reduce visibility to less than one mile.

* WHERE...Nearshore Gulf waters from the Walton-Okaloosa County
line to the Suwannee River out 20 nautical miles.

* WHEN...Until 9 AM EST /8 AM CST/ Wednesday.

* IMPACTS...Low visibility will make navigation difficult.
properties.instruction:
If you must navigate, proceed with caution. Use proper fog
signals. Make sure all running lights are on. Remember to use
your radar and compass.

NWSheadline: DENSE FOG ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 9 AM EST /8 AM CST/ WEDNESDAY
